{"tid":1957622,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"米高嘉道理爵士再撐年青人：「年青人是香港的未來 有責任給予他們希望」","createTime":"2020-04-04T05:10:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T11:40:48.000Z","uid":2054,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"87945422b28dd4181df483a945587f44190ede33","tid":1957622,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:10:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200402/N7DDLESNOOPD3RHCM7ETWYHKLQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200402%2FN7DDLESNOOPD3RHCM7ETWYHKLQ%2F&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQyrccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=fc84cb5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200402%2FN7DDLESNOOPD3RHCM7ETWYHKLQ%2F&h=497f5a29\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200402/N7DDLESNOOPD3RHCM7ETWYHKLQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n作風低調的大酒店（045）主席米高嘉道理，過往多次就香港社會事件發表意見，他於大酒店年報的主席序辭一欄中，以「年青人是香港的未來，本人深信他們當中有著世上最富的創造力和創意的人才。」為題，再次向大眾表示要為年青人創造希望，並稱對香港這個家，信心從未動搖。<br />\n米高嘉道理在文中提到：「於2019年回顧年內，本港市場經歷了近代史上其中一個最動盪的時期，發生了令人震驚的街頭衝突和社會動盪。目睹社會上出現嚴重分歧實在令人痛心不已，某些分歧恐怕可能需要幾個世代才能修補。」他又重提去年9月《致香港人的信》的內容，「我們堅信的香港精神，是透過尊重、瞭解和溝通，去尋求解決方法」，指出<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>「年青人是香港的未來，本人深信他們當中有著世上最富的創造力和創意的人才。」「政商界領袖有責任與年青人溝通交流，給予他們希望，並確保他們有機會實現更美好的未來。」</strong></span><br />\n米高嘉道理以身作則，他指集團定期與同事進行交流，當中包括與年輕一代員工對話，內容談及多方面的議題，自己亦攜同兒子斐歷一同參與集團舉行的同事交流大會，聽取來自不同背景和專業的員工對香港未來走向的洞察和見解。<br />\n文中除提及反修例運動外，亦提到現正侵襲全球的武漢肺炎，他表示，疫情的爆發對全世界造成巨大影響，公司對患者及其家屬深表同情，並對那些痛失至親的人寄以哀思。他續指，儘管香港發生社會動盪及受疫情影響，對香港這個家以及中國的長遠發展的信心仍然絲毫未變。"},{"pid":"522136a961525de5512e92b166d0ff63b654399b","tid":1957622,"uid":204539,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:12:40.000Z","msg":"role model of a true leader<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6efe066c33a451e48a957d9e0d3d3eaf8a3ee28a","tid":1957622,"uid":21470,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:12:41.000Z","msg":"有腦既都想悶聲發大財，邊個想行極左路線"},{"pid":"fa6414fd4454de0f53b624e996fffaf909f162e4","tid":1957622,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:14:13.000Z","msg":"香港人會記得邊個為我地發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7aedb404c628a787f9ff048f53b8b4a427a89a","tid":1957622,"uid":62020,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:15:26.000Z","msg":"中電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb97bc0fdcaa2d3c6f46ed34883dffe18f4231b0","tid":1957622,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b7aedb404c628a787f9ff048f53b8b4a427a89a","tid":1957622,"uid":62020,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:15:26.000Z","msg":"中電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:16:16.000Z","msg":"即刻入返幾手002<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa74442f6b07d2b13c147f46244470adb3b7f5a1","tid":1957622,"uid":62020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb97bc0fdcaa2d3c6f46ed34883dffe18f4231b0","tid":1957622,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b7aedb404c628a787f9ff048f53b8b4a427a89a","tid":1957622,"uid":62020,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:15:26.000Z","msg":"中電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:16:16.000Z","msg":"即刻入返幾手002<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:24:04.000Z","msg":"好多手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hk